ll>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>getSelection()</code></strong> property of the <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>DocumentOrShadowRoot</code></a> interface returns a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a> object representing the range of text selected by the user, or the current position of the caret.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var selection = documentOrShadowRootInstance.getSelection()\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"Returns","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a> object.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> selObj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSelection</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>selObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> selRange <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> selObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getRangeAt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// do stuff with the range</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notes","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"string_representation_of_the_selection_object","title":"String representation of the Selection object","isH3":true,"content":"<p>In JavaScript, when an object is passed to a function expecting a string (like <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/alert\"><code>Window.alert()</code></a>), the object's <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>toString()</code></a> method is called and the returned value is passed to the function. This can make the object appear to be a string when used with other functions when it is really an object with properties and methods.</p>\n<p>In the above example, <code>selObj.toString()</code> is automatically called when it is passed to <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/alert\"><code>Window.alert()</code></a>. However, attempting to use a JavaScript <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">String</a> property or method such as <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/length\"><code>length</code></a> or <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/substr\"><code>substr</code></a> directly on a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a> object results in an error if it does not have that property or method and may return unexpected results if it does. To use a <code>Selection</code> object as a string, call its <code>toString()</code> method directly:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> selectedText <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> selObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>selObj</code> is a <code>Selection</code> object.</li>\n  <li><code>selectedText</code> is a string (Selected text).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"related_objects","title":"Related objects","isH3":true,"content":"<p>HTML inputs provide simpler helper APIs for working with selection (see <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setSelectionRange\"><code>HTMLInputElement.setSelectionRange()</code></a>).</p>\n<p>Notice the difference between <em>selection</em> and <em>focus</em>. <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/activeElement\"><code>Document.activeElement</code></a> returns the focused element.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/selection-api/#dom-document-getselection","title":"Selection API"}],"query":"api.Document.getSelection"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Document.getSelection","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/getSelection/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Notes","id":"notes"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser Compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The getSelection() property of the DocumentOrShadowRoot interface returns a Selection object representing the range of text selected by the user, or the current position of the caret.","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.getSelection()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Document.getSelection()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"document.getSelection","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.getSelection()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document.getSelection()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Document.getSelection()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Document.getSelection()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/document/getselection","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/document/getselection/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/getSelection","title":"DocumentOrShadowRoot.getSelection()"}],"pageTitle":"DocumentOrShadowRoot.getSelection() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}